race.comment: PAW ULTRA (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Horsham in a handy 27.36 beating Springer's Boy. Form reads well for this. PAW FABIAN (3) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (29.55) over 515m at Sandown. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Ready to find winning form. PAW VINCE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (29.73) in a Grade 4/5 at Sandown. Form here sound including two wins. Should be thereabouts. PAW YANELLE (8) has claims fresh from a recent placing at this track and distance.
